snippet.title: Best VGM 855 - Brave Fencer Musashi - The White Cloud in the Sky
snippet.description:
A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

Playstation
Brave Fencer Musashi (1998)
The White Cloud in the Sky
Tsuyoshi Sekito
